    "description": {
      "value": "<em>With deft reflexes, you capitalize on opponents' mistake.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Dex 18, Combat Reflexes, Improved Unarmed Strike, Weapon Focus (unarmed strike); base attack bonus +16 or brawler level 12th.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>Once per round, when you are fighting unarmed with both hands free and an opponent misses you with a melee attack, it provokes an attack of opportunity from you. You must use an unarmed strike for this attack of opportunity.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>You can spend 5 stamina points to use this feat a second time during the same round.",
